divs: sighting detailsnever saw it until processing my photos 4421 crop at 200% first picture in a series 4422 crop at 200% second picture in a series first image resized complete image of the second picture of ufo above the car in picture. these were taken with a 5d mark ii & 24-105l lens at 28mm & 24mm at iso 200 & 1\1600s. i was not taking pictures of a ufo. i was only taking pictures of our snow around town. i took 20+ other pictures that show there isn't any artifacts on my lens or truck window. this also not lens flair caused by any light or sun hitting the truck windows or lens. taken at the corner of locust street & washington avenue in st. peter, mn. i am a wildlife & nature photographer by trade. i have raw images available upon request.
